### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "courier.candidate@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

> {% client.global.set("userId", response.body.id); %}

### 2. Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile/{{userId}}

### 3. Apply for Courier Role
POST http://localhost:8080/api/applications/apply/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to become a courier. I have a bike and I am very fast!"
}

> {% client.global.set("applicationId", response.body.id); %}

### 4. Admin: Get Pending Applications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/applications/pending

### 5. Admin: Approve Application
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/applications/{{applicationId}}/approve

### 6. Verify User Role Change (Should be COURIER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile/{{userId}}
